                                >ASCI 1795</ref>; <ref
                                target="https://archive.schoenberg.at/resources/pages/view.php?search=schenker&amp;k=&amp;modal=&amp;display=thumbs&amp;order_by=relevance&amp;offset=0&amp;per_page=48&amp;archive=&amp;sort=DESC&amp;restypes=1%2C2%2C5%2C6%2C7%2C8%2C9%2C12&amp;recentdaylimit=&amp;foredit=&amp;noreload=true&amp;access=&amp;ref=4275"
                                >ASCI 1479</ref>). Von <persName key="pers.1011">Hugo
                                Erfurth</persName> existieren vier Portraits, aufgenommen in
                                <placeName key="place.2.10">Dresden</placeName>, <date when="1912"
                                >1912;</date>
                            <ref
